      a(href='/api/symbols/ch.Modal.html') methods
      |  and
      a(href='/api/symbols/ch.Modal.html') properties.
      |  In this case, we are storing our modal window in the
      code myModal
      |  variable.
     
     p
      | The modal will have the next configuration:
     
     pre.code
      | var myModal = $("#modal").modal({
      |     content:"<p>This is a modal window with static content.</p>"
